                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>Sacramento</placeName>\n                <date>March 4/1856</date>\n            </p>\n            <p><addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee>!</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Dear Sir!</p>\n            <p>Enclosed you will find some<lb/> resolutions, which have been<lb/>\n                <sic>handet</sic> to me to forward to<lb/> you. You will address the three<lb/>\n                copies of the Occident to <persName>S. Hoffman</persName><lb/> It grieves me to\n                bring to notice<lb/> again that the Jewish Citizen<lb/> here are so neglecting as\n                not even<lb/> to come to (minyan) on <date><sic>Sabath</sic></date><lb/> and would\n                it not be for a few<lb/> which exert themselves, <sic>their</sic><lb/> would be\n                    <sic>non</sic> at all, and what<lb/> is the reason money their god<lb/> it would\n                please me greatly if you <lb/>would make a few remarks in<lb/> the Occident in\n                    <sic>regart</sic> to it.</p>\n            <p>The Occident is received here now<lb/> regularly and all parties are<lb/> satisfied\n                with it, as we like independent<lb/> Papers. Your agent <persName>I.\n                    Greenebaum</persName><lb/> is going to leave here on a trip</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3br8n24d/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
