                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>to the states on the <date>20<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi></date> of this<lb/> hoping that\n                this will reach<lb/> you in good health and<lb/> accept the best wishes of your\n                friend</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">N. Hoshland</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p>NB If it should require a signature<lb/> to the communication in regard<lb/> to the\n                jewish nos coming to the<lb/> synagogue. please and sign it\n                (<persName>N.</persName>)</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(4)\">\n                <del>\n                    <add>?</add>\n                </del>\n            </p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
